    {
      "question": "<p>Quel est le <u>coefficient directeur</u> de la fonction lin&eacute;aire repr&eacute;sent&eacute;e ?</p>\n<p><img src=\"img/exemple.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "explain": "<p>La fonction est lin&eacute;aire donc de la forme : <span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><u><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\">f(</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Cambria Math',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Cambria Math'; color: black;\">𝑥</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\">) = a</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Cambria Math',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Cambria Math'; color: black;\">𝑥.</span></u></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\">On cherche &agrave; d&eacute;terminer a. Si </span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Cambria Math',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Cambria Math'; color: black;\">𝑥</span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\"> = 2, alors f(2) = 6. On peut &eacute;crire <u>f(2) = a &times; 2 = 6</u>, d'o&ugrave; a = 6/2 = 3. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\"><u>Le coefficient directeur est 3.</u></span></p>",
      "choices": [
        "0",
        "1",
        "2",
        "*3"
      ],
      "type": "choices",
      "steps": [],
      "id": "math/60.15"
