      "type": "choices",
      "steps": [],
      "id": "math/60.19"
    },
    {
      "question": "<p>On a repr&eacute;sent&eacute; la fonction lin&eacute;aire :&nbsp;<u><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">f(</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Cambria Math', serif;\">𝑥</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">) = 2</span></u><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Cambria Math', serif;\"><u>𝑥</u>.</span></p>\n<p>Par quel point la droite passe-t-elle ?</p>\n<p><img src=\"img/question2.png\" /></p>",
      "explain": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\">Si </span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Cambria Math',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Cambria Math'; color: black;\">𝑥</span><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\"> = 1, alors f(1) = 2&times;1 = 2. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; color: black;\">Donc, la droite <u>passe par le point (1 ; 2)</u>.</span></p>",
